title: Team Sprint Planning
agenda_items: Define user stories (10 min), Estimate story points (15 min), Plan sprint backlog (15 min), Set sprint goals (5 min)

title: Weekly Standup
agenda_items: Yesterday's progress (5 min), Today's goals (5 min), Blockers discussion (3 min), Next steps (2 min)

title: Client Quarterly Review
agenda_items: Welcome and introductions (5 min), Q4 achievements overview (20 min), Product demo (25 min), Q&A and feedback (10 min)

title: Product Design Workshop
agenda_items: Problem identification (15 min), User research insights (20 min), Ideation session (30 min), Solution prioritization (15 min), Next steps planning (10 min)

title: Marketing Campaign Planning
agenda_items: Campaign objectives (10 min), Target audience analysis (15 min), Content strategy brainstorm (20 min), Timeline and budget (5 min)

title: Customer Feedback Session
agenda_items: Customer introductions (5 min), Product feedback collection (25 min), Feature requests discussion (10 min)
